Parameters.Name: pLogoutput
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Write parameters and action summary to server message log (Boolean True = 1)

Parameters.Name: pCube
Parameters.Prompt: REQUIRED: Cube name

Parameters.Name: pView
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Temporary view name

Parameters.Name: pFilter
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Filter: Year¦ 2006 + 2007 & Scenario¦ Actual + Budget & Organization¦ North America Operations (Blank=whole cube)

Parameters.Name: pFilterParallel
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Parallelization Filter: Month:Q1+Q2+Q3+Q4 (Blank=run single threaded). Single dimension parallel slices. Will be added to filter single element at a time. Dimension must not be part of filter

Parameters.Name: pParallelThreads
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Maximum number of threads to run when parallel processing is enabled ( if <2 will execute one thread, but parallel filter is still applied )

Parameters.Name: pDimDelim
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Delimiter between dimensions  (default value if blank = '&')

Parameters.Name: pEleStartDelim
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Delimiter for start of element list  (default value if blank = '¦')

Parameters.Name: pEleDelim
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Delimiter between elements  (default value if blank = '+')

Parameters.Name: pSuppressZero
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Suppress Zero Values (1=Suppress)

Parameters.Name: pSuppressConsol
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Suppress Consolidated Values? (1=Suppress)

Parameters.Name: pSuppressRules
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Suppress Rule Values? (1=Suppress)

Parameters.Name: pZeroSource
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Zero Out view AFTER Copy? (Boolean 1=True)

Parameters.Name: pCubeLogging
Parameters.Prompt: Required: Cube Logging (0 = No transaction logging, 1 = Logging of transactions, 2 = Ignore Cube Logging - No Action Taken)

Parameters.Name: pTemp
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Retain temporary view and Subset ( 0 = retain View and Subsets 1 = use temp objects)

Parameters.Name: pFilePath
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Export Directory (will default to error file path)

Parameters.Name: pFileName
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Export Filename (If Left Blank Defaults to cube_export.csv)

Parameters.Name: pDelim
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: AsciiOutput delimiter character (Default=comma, exactly 3 digits = ASCII code)

Parameters.Name: pQuote
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: AsciiOutput quote character (Accepts empty quote, exactly 3 digits = ASCII code)

Parameters.Name: pTitleRecord
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Include Title Record in Export File? (Boolean 0=false, 1=true, 2=title and filter line Default=1)

Parameters.Name: pSandbox
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: To use sandbox not base data enter the sandbox name (invalid name will result in process error)

Parameters.Name: pSuppressConsolStrings
Parameters.Prompt: OPTIONAL: Suppress Strings on Consolidations (Skip = 1) (Default = 0)
